channel.description:
[center][size=36pt]Project - Enrisep![/size][/center]
[center][size=14pt]Its clean, but added some good things, and fixed some bugs. Good for beginners.[/size][/center]
100% Duper Free, and dupes are fixed. Trade dupe fixed. Log out dupe fixed. Duel arena 2 dupe's fixed. Arrow dupe fixed. Xlog fixed. And more.
Fixed some combat bugs.
Added working xp orb.
Fixed log out bug.
Fixed lunar interface.
Added some shits, like extreme donator zone, super zone, and donator zone. ::edz ::sdz ::dz.
Added skillzone with objects and shops.
Fixed some equip item slots.
Added some customs, like chaotic, and primal.
Clean Quest Tab.
Added ::yell.
Added donator rank, and symbol.
Added full screen at client! with 474 revision!
Thieving now give's you scrolls, so then you thiev it, click on the crate behind the stalls, and you will receive cash !
And more!

item.dc:creator: @g2uypie g2uypie
item.description:
@g2uypie wrote:

I’m having a little trouble with the Client launcher. I have the newest JDK and JRE.

I run it and get the following error:

Any assistance would be awesome!

EDIT: The batch window closes immediately after opening, so I had to screen shot it quick. I’m completely lost on this one.

Here’s the batch script:

@echo off
title Project-Enrisep  - Loading
color 0a

:start
echo.
echo -
echo Project-Enrisep Starting up...
echo -
if exist "%HOMEDRIVE%\Program Files (x86)"  goto x64
goto x86


:x64
title  Project-Enrisep (x64) - Loader
echo Auto-Detected 64-bit (x64) System
echo -
echo Client Output will be below
echo -
echo.
"%HOMEDRIVE%/Program Files (x86)/Java/jre7/bin/java.exe" -Xmx1000m client
exit


:x86
title  Project-Enrisep (x86) - Loader
echo Auto-Detected 32-bit (x86) System
echo -
echo Client Output will be below
echo -
echo.
"%HOMEDRIVE%/Program Files/Java/jre7/bin/java.exe" -Xmx1000m client
pause
